		<legis-type>A BILL</legis-type>
		<official-title>To amend the Internal Revenue Code of 1986 to provide for
		  a refundable adoption tax credit.</official-title>
	</form>
	<legis-body>
		<section id="S1" section-type="section-one">
      <enum>1.</enum>
      <header>Short
			 title</header>
      <text display-inline="no-display-inline">This Act may be cited as
			 the <quote>
          <short-title>Adoption Tax Credit Refundability
			 Act of 2013</short-title>
        </quote>.</text>
		</section>
    <section id="id7FCC687AB8144DBAA90EFFEC4F01A777">
      <enum>2.</enum>
      <header>Refundable
			 adoption tax credit</header>
			<subsection id="id14317D48104B432CB8D86552DB4664C0">
        <enum>(a)</enum>
        <header>Credit made
			 refundable</header>
				<paragraph id="id2C2C3656FCD64640A014996D54A6DE37">
          <enum>(1)</enum>
          <header>Credit moved to
			 subpart relating to refundable credits</header>
          <text>The <cato:entity-ref xmlns:cato="http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml" entity-type="act" value="Internal Revenue Code of 1986">Internal Revenue Code
			 of 1986</cato:entity-ref> is amended—</text>
					<subparagraph id="H59F7A7756D4A418693EF75B56BF3E85E">
            <enum>(A)</enum>
            <text>by redesignating
			 <cato:entity-ref xmlns:cato="http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml" entity-type="act" value="Internal Revenue Code of 1986/s:23">section 23</cato:entity-ref> as <cato:entity-ref xmlns:cato="http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml" entity-type="act" value="Internal Revenue Code of 1986/s:36C" proposed="true">section 36C</cato:entity-ref>, and</text>
					</subparagraph>
          <subparagraph id="HF8ED74BE347B486497C36B4A4A2ED22A">
            <enum>(B)</enum>
            <text>by moving <cato:entity-ref xmlns:cato="http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml" entity-type="act" value="Internal Revenue Code of 1986/s:36C" proposed="true">section
			 36C</cato:entity-ref> (as so redesignated) from <cato:entity-ref xmlns:cato="http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml" entity-type="act" value="Internal Revenue Code of 1986/ch:1/sch:A/pt:IV/spt:A">subpart A of part IV of subchapter A of chapter 1</cato:entity-ref>
			 to the location immediately before <cato:entity-ref xmlns:cato="http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml" entity-type="act" value="Internal Revenue Code of 1986/ch:1/sch:A/pt:IV/spt:C/s:37">section 37 in subpart C of part IV of
			 subchapter A of chapter 1</cato:entity-ref>.</text>
					</subparagraph>
        </paragraph>
        <paragraph id="id3678D86A5A8444608D1CEA9D84CE4CA0">
          <enum>(2)</enum>
          <header>Conforming
			 Amendments</header>
					<subparagraph id="H3F47EFD3CA094072AC46066DC5E9FC18">
            <enum>(A)</enum>
            <text>
